statements.select: select * from PCPGOnlineCheck where PCPGOnlineCheckId in(select p.PCPGOnlineCheckId from PCPGOnlineCheck p left join PCPGOnlineCheckDetail pd on pd.PCPGOnlineCheckId=p.PCPGOnlineCheckId left join PronoteHeader ph on pd.FromInvoiceId=ph.PronoteHeaderID left join ProduceOtherCompact pc on pd.FromInvoiceId=pc.ProduceOtherCompactId where 1=1 $SQL$
